Package foundation

Class Assignment

java.lang.Object
foundation.Assignment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Assignment extends Object implements Serializable
Instances of this class will store information pertaining to individual assignments. It stores the name, description, type, possible points, grade, and due date.
Author:
william
